div.p:
"Then,
if it is agreeable to you, ma'am, I will stay. To be sure the place is dull;
but I have got a good mistress — and" —

"What would you do?" cried she. "Madman, would you hang for them and break my heart;
the only woman in the world that loves you.  Give me the pistol. Nay,
I will have it."
